I am a huge Cantinflas fan and this was one of the movies I had yet to see. It was hilarious. I will be watching it over and over again with my family.
Nothing like enjoying a good laugh with family seeing and hearing typical Cantinflas performance in one of his old movies

The quality of the movie/dvd was excellent considering the movies were filmed over 50 years.  At first, I was not sure how they would turn out, however the quality and both movies were great ... brought back good memories.
Got this for a friend of mine, she is so happy to be able to find these movies online, their things she hasn't watched in a long time and she loves them.

My parents are 90 and 95. They totally LOVE these CLASSIC Mexican movies.
With Cantinflas you can never go wrong. Hilarious comedy.
beautiful movie, just love it!!!

This amazing movie brings together the talent of 3 of Mexico's greatest comedians of all time: Mario Moreno, Joaquin Pardav and Sara Garcia in a hilariously twisted tale of misunderstandings and family "misfortune". Definitely a most see movie for any foreign comedy enthusiast!
This double feature of one of Mexico's most beloved comedians is truly a classic to be viewed. Thanks for making this dvd available as its hard to find these here in Tampa. A+ price and service.

Just received this two movie set but was disappointed to see that you have to flip the dvd to watch the other movie.  I have received two movie sets for Cantinflas from other companies and they have both the movies on the same side - even engravings of the movies on the top side.  This was just a blank dvd - not even any pictures - just little writing around the center hole.  But the quality was good and both movies were great as expected.
